 stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star fill-[#ffdcc2]\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><span>8.5</span></div></div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold leading-tight line-clamp-1 text-white mb-1\">Clarkson&#x27;s Farm</h3></div><div style=\"height:0px;opacity:0\"><div class=\"px-4 pb-4\"><p class=\"text-xs text-neutral-300 line-clamp-3 leading-relaxed mb-4\">Follow Jeremy Clarkson as he embarks on his latest adventure, farming. The man who on several occasions claims to be allergic to manual labour takes on the most manually labour intensive job there is. What could possibly go wrong?</p><div class=\"w-full py-3 rounded-xl bg-[#c3f0c2] text-[#07210b] font-bold text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:brightness-110 transition-all active:scale-[0.98]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-play fill-[#07210b]\"><polygon points=\"6 3 20 12 6 21 6 3\"></polygon></svg><span>Watch Now</span></div></div></div></div></a><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 right-4 z-50 flex justify-between items-start pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md text-black text-[11px] font-black px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg\">2021</div><button class=\"\n            pointer-events-auto  /* &lt;--- ADD THIS HERE */\n            w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full shadow-lg border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-md transition-colors duration-200 cursor