ound\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star fill-[#ffdcc2]\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><span>4.2</span></div></div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold leading-tight line-clamp-1 text-white mb-1\">Never-Ending Summer</h3></div><div style=\"height:0px;opacity:0\"><div class=\"px-4 pb-4\"><p class=\"text-xs text-neutral-300 line-clamp-3 leading-relaxed mb-4\">To save her gravely ill grandmother, top student Zhou Wan approaches her mother&#x27;s stepson, Lu Xixiao, for funds. They fall for each other over the summer after graduation but are torn apart by misunderstandings in reality. Ten years later, they reunite at work. Though Lu Xixiao harbors resentment, his love for Zhou Wan remains. As they uncover the truth behind a &quot;factory accident,&quot; they resolve their differences and reunite.</p><div class=\"w-full py-3 rounded-xl bg-[#c3f0c2] text-[#07210b] font-bold text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:brightness-110 transition-all active:scale-[0.98]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-play fill-[#07210b]\"><polygon points=\"6 3 20 12 6 21 6 3\"></polygon></svg><span>Watch Now</span></div></div></div></div></a><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 right-4 z-50 flex justify-between items-start pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md text-black text-[11px] font-black px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg\">2026</div><button class=\"\n            pointer-events-auto  /* &lt;---