tudent, is on his way home from the convenience store when he finds  himself transported to another world. As he's lost and confused in a new  world where he doesn't even know left from right, the only person to  reach out to him was a beautiful girl with silver hair. Determined to  repay her somehow for saving him from his own despair, Subaru agrees to  help the girl find something she's looking for.\",\"poster_path\":\"/5MrRCj7z92YLWMXHeWKp19eJPYv.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"ja\",\"genre_ids\":[16,10759,10765,18,9648],\"popularity\":80.2799,\"first_air_date\":\"2016-04-04\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":7.916,\"vote_count\":657,\"origin_country\":[\"JP\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/vyG93jhmPL7tBIhRtCLa5mdBKob.jpg\",\"id\":276161,\"name\":\"Teach You a Lesson\",\"original_name\":\"참교육\",\"overview\":\"An inspector from the Educational Rights Protection Bureau (ERPB) who is authorized by the government to use physical intervention and unconventional methods to discipline delinquent students and reform the educational system.\",\"poster_path\":\"/fMECSPrTmRClSViMsXFYmiYIcWP.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"ko\",\"genre_ids\":[10759,18,35],\"popularity\":251.2123,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-06-05\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":9.5,\"vote_count\":344,\"origin_country\":[\"KR\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/m7eiSGHFzr584zFmetGqkqaU6BN.jpg\",\"id\":124364,\"name\":\"FROM\",\"original_name\":\"FROM\",\"overview\":\"Unravel the mystery of a nightmarish town in middle America that traps all those who enter. As the unwilling residents fight to keep a sense of normalcy and search for a way out, they must also survive the threats of the surrounding forest – including the terrifying creatures that come out when the sun goes down.\",\"poster_path\":\"/pRtJagIxpfODzzb0T0NAvZSzErC.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[9648,18,10765],\"popularity\":722.4397,\"first_air_date\":\"2022-02-20\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.478,\"vote_count\":3669,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/2rmK7mnchw9Xr3XdiTFSxTTLXqv.jpg\",\"id\":37854,\"name\":\"One Piece\",\"original_name\":\"ワンピース\",\"overview\":\"Years ago, the fearsome Pirate King, Gol D. Roger was executed leaving a huge pile of treasure and the famous \\\"One Piece\\\" behind. Whoever claims the \\\"One Piece\\\" will be named the new King of the Pirates.\\n\\nMonkey D. Luffy, a boy who consumed a \\\"Devil Fruit,\\\" decides to follow in the footsteps of his idol, the pirate Shanks, and find the One Piece. It helps, of course, that his body has the properties of rubber and that he's surrounded by a bevy of skilled fighters and thieves to help him along the way.\\n\\nLuffy will do anything to get the One Piece and become King of the Pirates!\",\"poster_path\":\"/dB4EDhre2dsC2kxYDavyKWqLQwi.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"ja\",\"genre_ids\":[10759,35,16],\"popularity\":41.8598,\"first_air_date\":\"1999-10-20\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.7,\"vote_count\":5357,\"origin_country\":[\"JP\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/jIArNHIekrCSVgdMbKPAXpPY03Y.jpg\",\"id\":456,\"name\":\"The Simpsons\",\"original_name\":\"The Simpsons\",\"overview\":\"Set in Springfield, the average American town, the show focuses on the antics and everyday adventures of the Simpson family; Homer, Marge, Bart, Lisa and Maggie, as well as a virtual cast of thousands. Since the beginning, the series has been a pop culture icon, attracting hundreds of celebrities to guest star. The show has also made name for itself in its fearless satirical take on politics, media and American life in general.\",\"poster_path\":\"/uWpG7GqfKGQqX4YMAo3nv5OrglV.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[10751,16,35],\"popularity\":174.1698,\"first_air_date\":\"1989-12-17\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.019,\"vote_count\":10825,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/hGCQ0tsJMpKjfrnCyYY0kMY2kY1.jpg\",\"id\":322430,\"name\":\"The Polygamist\",\"original_name\":\"The Polygamist\",\"overview\":\"Social media darling, Joyce, is the picture of marital perfection — until her cheating husband's conquests ignite a scandalous emotional meltdown.\",\"poster_path\":\"/3VEHSG9ZCWcTGbU2ciiU6iDzemP.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"zu\",\"genre_ids\":[18,10766],\"popularity\":139.8587,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-06-12\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":6.464,\"vote_count\":14,\"origin_country\":[\"ZA\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/i50h4Gz6e9BMGak5l6gg5qfIjcv.jpg\",\"id\":117648,\"name\":\"Clarkson's Farm\",\"original_name\":\"Clarkson's Farm\",\"overview\":\"Follow Jeremy Clarkson as he embarks on his latest adventure, farming. The man who on several occasions claims to be allergic to manual labour takes on the most manually labour intensive job there is. What could possibly go wrong?\",\"poster_path\":\"/toVhyqMT3ICfahE7Ad8obJvZHpX.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[10764,35],\"popularity\":59.2478,\"first_air_date\":\"2021-06-11\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.49,\"vote_count\":415,\"origin_country\":[\"GB\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/s8aroz7KFG4vUBR7JJfmPHRaQV7.jpg\",\"id\":321623,\"name\":\"The Season\",\"original_name\":\"The Season\",\"overview\":\"A group of friends in Hong Kong's elite boating scene find their summer getaway descending into betrayal and power plays as hidden agendas surface.\",\"poster_path\":\"/kPz9M2hbZVRue9bbZAHKB9RrXox.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"popularity\":7.6074,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-06-17\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":10,\"vote_count\":1,\"origin_country\":[\"HK\",\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/577eXC8wFQT0eUrJcgznSiFPRmk.jpg\",\"id\":94997,\"name\":\"House of the Dragon\",\"original_name\":\"House of the Dragon\",\"overview\":\"The Targaryen dynasty is at the absolute apex of its power, with more than 15 dragons under their yoke. Most empires crumble from such heights. In the case of the Targaryens, their slow fall begins when King Viserys breaks with a century of tradition by naming his daughter Rhaenyra heir to the Iron Throne. But when Viserys later fathers a son, the court is shocked when Rhaenyra retains her status as his heir, and seeds of division sow friction across the realm.\",\"poster_path\":\"/7V0Ebks0GgpKvQ7QbLAIdX5dos4.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[10765,18,10759],\"popularity\":103.4892,\"first_air_date\":\"2022-08-21\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.298,\"vote_count\":6031,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/mkwVoyP9bFSmfVqU8FJyem52hVR.jpg\",\"id\":220102,\"name\":\"Spider-Noir\",\"original_name\":\"Spider-Noir\",\"overview\":\"Ben Reilly, an aging and down on his luck private investigator in 1930s New York, is forced to grapple with his past life as the city's one and only superhero.\",\"poster_path\":\"/oD8WSVqz84ZRfelkr7JPeJwR9Iv.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[18,9648,80],\"popularity\":116.9875,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-05-25\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.556,\"vote_count\":541,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/80vo7eYhAXPJltu32lG5JGrGPzG.jpg\",\"id\":288603,\"name\":\"Never-Ending Summer\",\"original_name\":\"炽夏\",\"overview\":\"To save her gravely ill grandmother, top student Zhou Wan approaches her mother's stepson, Lu Xixiao, for funds. They fall for each other over the summer after graduation but are torn apart by misunderstandings in reality. Ten years later, they reunite at work. Though Lu Xixiao harbors resentment, his love for Zhou Wan remains. As they uncover the truth behind a \\\"factory accident,\\\" they resolve their differences and reunite.\",\"poster_path\":\"/9bB4tJbjViEsQCMJ0qth7wuzpNA.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"zh\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"popularity\":146.5872,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-06-16\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":4.2,\"vote_count\":2,\"origin_country\":[\"CN\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/n6vVs6z8obNbExdD3QHTr4Utu1Z.jpg\",\"id\":76479,\"name\":\"The Boys\",\"original_name\":\"The Boys\",\"overview\":\"A group of vigilantes known informally as “The Boys” set out to take down corrupt superheroes with no more than blue-collar grit and a willingness to fight dirty.\",\"poster_path\":\"/in1R2dDc421JxsoRWaIIAqVI2KE.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[10765,10759],\"popularity\":273.7089,\"first_air_date\":\"2019-07-25\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.451,\"vote_count\":12938,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/9In9QgVJx7PlFOAgVHCKKSbo605.jpg\",\"id\":60625,\"name\":\"Rick and Morty\",\"original_name\":\"Rick and Morty\",\"overview\":\"Follows a sociopathic genius scientist who drags his inherently timid grandson on adventures across the universe.\",\"poster_path\":\"/owhkU6KRqdXoUQpjV8uyZGPtX58.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[16,35,10765,10759],\"popularity\":144.1739,\"first_air_date\":\"2013-12-02\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.679,\"vote_count\":10986,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/qCGwPCwlSiLdlYinzy9rSQDjQX1.jpg\",\"id\":135934,\"name\":\"The Legend of Vox Machina\",\"original_name\":\"The Legend of Vox Machina\",\"overview\":\"They're rowdy, they're ragtag, they're misfits turned mercenaries for hire. Vox Machina is more interested in easy money and cheap ale than actually protecting the realm. But when the kingdom is threatened by evil, this boisterous crew realizes that they are the only ones capable of restoring justice.\",\"poster_path\":\"/zjQTSYZEmy0GVnK1aFLvNiAwluo.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[16,10765,10759],\"popularity\":40.4631,\"first_air_date\":\"2022-01-27\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8.196,\"vote_count\":649,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/p8ct9P4pazzP85HMVhWbnlJw8D1.jpg\",\"id\":325583,\"name\":\"Eclipse of Illusion SP：The Miasma War\",\"original_name\":\"云深不知梦 特别篇：逐冥之役\",\"overview\":\"\",\"poster_path\":\"/jewlUepfUnqurE9xdj80RXIR52k.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"zh\",\"genre_ids\":[16,10765],\"popularity\":2.3536,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-06-17\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":7,\"vote_count\":1,\"origin_country\":[\"CN\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/52sp0vPhLOWrZ1QoZIWiapronM.jpg\",\"id\":273240,\"name\":\"Off Campus\",\"original_name\":\"Off Campus\",\"overview\":\"Hannah Wells tutors hockey captain Garrett Graham to win over her crush. Their deal becomes real connection as they face their pasts. Friends Logan, Dean, Tucker, and Allie navigate college life and love.\",\"poster_path\":\"/cbODFqkcmRgrYH8NkG4Q4Hcg8Z1.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"popularity\":327.1642,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-05-13\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":9,\"vote_count\":469,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/65K3llBL0wlW0C3pNaQyjWOdwbp.jpg\",\"id\":302658,\"name\":\"Founder: Orhan\",\"original_name\":\"Kuruluş: Orhan\",\"overview\":\"Kuruluş: Orhan is a Turkish historical drama that follows the life of Orhan Bey, the son of Osman I and the second ruler of the Ottoman Empire. Set in the 14th century, the series portrays Orhan’s transformation from a young warrior into a visionary leader who expands his father's legacy by conquering key Byzantine cities like Bursa and establishing the foundations of a powerful empire. With political intrigue, epic battles, and complex relationships, the show explores Orhan’s rise amidst internal strife and external threats, continuing the legacy of Kuruluş: Osman with a new generation of characters and high-stakes storytelling.\",\"poster_path\":\"/1kEgzEvhJmw5eSxuGwn0o1cgHlK.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"tr\",\"genre_ids\":[18,10759,10768],\"popularity\":24.7604,\"first_air_date\":\"2025-10-29\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":8,\"vote_count\":5,\"origin_country\":[\"TR\"]},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/wh5agdl3b7fqC7mSjsCkHx4fMAs.jpg\",\"id\":299167,\"name\":\"Dutton Ranch\",\"original_name\":\"Dutton Ranch\",\"overview\":\"Rip Wheeler and Beth Dutton gamble everything on a new life in South Texas, but the promise of building a future far from the ghosts of Yellowstone quickly collides with brutal new realities and a rival ranch that will stop at nothing to protect its empire.\",\"poster_path\":\"/xsiecCxd8lkcAluw0wWwbW5CwSv.jpg\",\"media_type\":\"tv\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"genre_ids\":[37,18],\"popularity\":142.5625,\"first_air_date\":\"2026-05-15\",\"softcore\":false,\"vote_average\":9.345,\"vote_count\":275,\"origin_country\":[\"US\"]}]}]\n","segmentData":{"/_tree":":HL[\"/_next/static/chunks/0-32plc7q7dqy.css\",\"style\"]\n0:{\"tree\":{\"name\":\"\",\"param\":null,\"prefetchHints\":16,\"slots\":{\"children\":{\"name\":\"series\",\"param\":null,\"prefetchHints\":0,\"slots\":{\"children\":{\"name\":\"__PAGE__\",\"param\":null,\"prefetchHints\":0,\"slots\":null}}}}},\"staleTime\":300,\"buildId\":\"FupozjRAk1PGzjdmOUWEN\"}\n","/_full":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[3541,[\"/_next/static/chunks/2gr4rjfntu8nf.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ngfym8huajzf.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/2kkesr-tzm91x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/314o2p8-gaysn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0nyxha5q3r9ys.js\"],\"\"]\n3:I[10825,[\"/_next/static/chunks/2gr4rjfntu8nf.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ngfym8huajzf.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/2kkesr-tzm91x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/314o2p8-gaysn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0nyxha5q3r9ys.js\"],\"default\"]\n4:I[39756,[\"/_next/static/chun